         Trace wins: Paley 5, Interval 5 (of 11 odd k values)
  p=31: c_5 Paley=151032, Interval=142352, diff=+8680
         c_7/7 Paley=24414360, Interval=25316212, diff=-901852
         Trace wins: Paley 7, Interval 7 (of 15 odd k values)

